          <title>
            <string language="en">Women's History Month</string>
            <string language="x-mt-de">Monat Geschichte Der Frauen</string>
            <string language="x-mt-fr">Mois de l'Histoire des Femmes</string>
            <string language="x-mt-pt">Mês Do History Das Mulheres</string>
            <string language="x-mt-it">Mese Di Storia Delle Donne</string>
            <string language="x-mt-el">Μήνας ιστορίας γυναικών</string>
            <string language="x-mt-es">Mes De la Historia De las Mujeres</string>
          </title>
          <description>
            <string language="en">showcases historic properties that illustrate contributions of women to our nation's history. Harriet Beecher Stowe, Eleanor Ford, Amelia Earhart, Mary McLeod Bethune, and are among those featured.</string>
          </description>
          <keyword>
            <string language="en">Social Sciences</string>
          </keyword>
          <language>en</language>
          <description>
            <string language="x-mt-de">stellt historische Eigenschaften zur Schau, die 
Beiträge der Frauen zur Geschichte unserer Nation veranschaulichen. 
Harriet Beecher Stowe, Eleanor Ford, Amelia Earhart, Mary McLeod
Bethune und gehören zu gekennzeichneten denen.</string>
          </description>
          <description>
            <string language="x-mt-fr">présente les propriétés historiques qui 
illustrent des contributions des femmes à l'histoire de notre nation.
Harriet Beecher Stowe, Eleanor Ford, Amelia Earhart, Mary McLeod
Bethune, et sont parmi ceux décrits.</string>
          </description>
          <description>
            <string language="x-mt-pt">showcases as propriedades historic que ilustram 
contribuições das mulheres ao history da nossa nação. 
Harriet Beecher Stowe, Eleanor Ford, Amelia Earhart, Mary McLeod
Bethune, e é entre aqueles caracterizados.</string>
          </description>
          <description>
            <string language="x-mt-it">montra le proprietà storiche che 
illustrano i contributi delle donne a storia della nostra nazione. 
Harriet Beecher Stowe, Eleanor Ford, Amelia Earhart, Mary McLeod
Bethune ed è fra quelli descritti.</string>
          </description>
          <description>
            <string language="x-mt-el">επιδεικνύει τις ιστορικές ιδιότητες που επεξηγούν τις 
συνεισφορές των γυναικών στην ιστορία του έθνους μας. Ο 
Harriet Beecher Stowe, Eleanor διάβαση, Amelia 
Earhart, Mary McLeod Bethune, και είναι εκείνων που 
χαρακτηρίζονται μεταξύ.</string>
          </description>
          <description>
            <string language="x-mt-es">showcases las características históricas que 
ilustran contribuciones de mujeres a la historia de nuestra nación. 
Harriet Beecher Stowe, Eleanor Ford, Amelia Earhart, Maria 
McLeod Bethune, y está entre ésos ofrecidos.</string>
          </description>
